Part I : Run
1. To Compile:
    $ make
2. To Run:
    $ ./a.out

Part II : Configuration
1. Set Resolution, Change Value Of Following Variable.
    line 280    num_of_pixel_x
    line 281    num_of_pixel_y
    line 282    max_depth 

2. Set Step Direction, Change Following Variable
    line 287 - line 305
    uncomment the line satisfy the requirement

3. Set Phong Flag, Change Following Variable
    line 312    bool phong_flag

4. Change Image Name
    line 328    fp = fopen(ImageName, "wb");

5. Change Initial Location For Ray Casting
    line 359 - 374
    uncomment the line satisfy the requirement

6. Change Scalar Value Used
    line 394 for heart data set
    line 397 for earth mantle data

7. Change Gradient Used By Phong
    line 411 for heart data set
    line 416 for earth mantle data

8. Change Light Position For Phong
    line 426 - line 431 for earth mantle data
    line 437 - line 441 for earth mantle data

